		"Id": "mechdef_salamander_PPR-OG",
		"Name": "Orga",
		"Details": "This 'Mech, piloted by a masked MechWarrior with an unknown identity, was nicknamed 'Orga' after a creature from an ancient Terran kaiju tri-vid. The pilot seemingly loves these sorts of things, though their second (and more important) love appears to be clouds of missiles, something that Orga manages just fine. Orga is fairly conventional in construction, with an XL Engine, XL Gyro, and Endo-Steel frame, but for firepower it uses paired Apollo-enabled MRM-40 launchers. Ten tons of CASE II protected ammo keep it secure in combat and a multi-trac FCS gives it the ability to split fire when necessary in combat, helping it truly earn its fan-granted title of the Battle Royale Beast.\n\n <b><color=#e51717>COMMUNITY CONTENT</color></b>",
		"Icon": "uixTxrIcon_salamander"
	},
